Use this exact checklist now:

curl -i http://localhost:8081/index.php/apps/openidconnect/config
curl -i http://localhost:8081/.well-known/openid-configuration
curl -iL http://localhost:8081/.well-known/openid-configuration

How to read them:

302 to /login = broken for discovery
200 + application/json = good
200 but HTML login page = still broken
404 = missing rewrite/proxy rule
500 = app/config problem inside ownCloud